# Custom Widgets — Quick Reference

All widgets defined under `passages/0 - System/Widgets/`. Listed by domain. Call from any passage: `<<widgetName arg1 arg2>>`.

## Time (`TimeWidgets.twee`)

| Widget | Signature | Purpose |
|--------|-----------|---------|
| `<<advanceTime>>` | `minutes: Number` | Advance clock, run all decay/schedule hooks |
| `<<updateCharacterLocations>>` | (no args) | Recompute `$characters[].currentLocation` from schedule |
| `<<getPeriod>>` | (no args) | Return "morning"/"afternoon"/"evening"/"night" for current time |

## Stats (`StatCalculator.twee`, `StatNotifications.twee`)

| Widget | Signature | Purpose |
|--------|-----------|---------|
| `<<gainStat>>` | `statName: String, amount: Number` | +stat, clamp, toast notification |
| `<<loseStat>>` | `statName: String, amount: Number` | −stat, clamp, toast |
| `<<updateDerivedStats>>` | (no args) | Recompute attractiveness, mood, etc. |

